{"tid":1294484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[恐怖慎入] 軟巢行動：中國滲透全球電信網路的計畫","createTime":"2019-07-07T19:17:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T10:44:39.000Z","uid":260806,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3e819b1b44f3d9ac3acb0f68d580488571afcd88","tid":1294484,"uid":260806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T19:17:35.000Z","msg":"在2018年，Cybereason Nocturnus 團隊發現了針對全球電信商的<span style=\"color: red;\">進階持續性攻擊</span> (APT - Advanced Persistent Threat 詳見下註)，此攻擊模式使用與<span style=\"color: red;\">中國駭客組織APT10</span>相關的工具和技術。這種多波攻擊的重點是獲取特定高價值目標的數據，最後完全接管網絡。<br />\n<br />\n註：APT攻擊。APT全名為Advanced Persistent Threat，中文一般譯為<span style=\"color: red;\">進階持續性威脅</span>（攻擊）。簡單來說，攻擊者會先收集攻擊對象的生活習性，依據他的生活習性，設計入侵的方式，並編寫防毒軟體都抓不到的客製化攻擊程式；一旦入侵成功，掌握了機器，就能以這個機器作為節點，繼續收集更多資料，尋找下一個攻擊目標。這些攻擊可能會從周圍的攻擊對象下手，逐步進逼到核心目標。最終，控制了關鍵裝置後，就能取得關鍵機敏資訊，或是發起攻擊以中斷服務；最後，把自己留下的資訊與足跡消除，避免自己被找到。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ihpn2-4jTvc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIhpn2-4jTvc&d=Tc8prIKBo9hF1z3tnQ%2BJRtHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=a7053c79\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ihpn2-4jTvc</a><br />\n英文資料：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cybereason.com/blog/operation-soft-cell-a-worldwide-campaign-against-telecommunications-providers\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cybereason.com%2Fblog%2Foperation-soft-cell-a-worldwide-campaign-against-telecommunications-providers&d=Tc8prIKBo9hF1z3tnQ%2BJRtHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=cfcd14c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cybereason.com/blog/operation-soft-cell-a-worldwide-campaign-against-telecommunications-providers</a><br />\n<br />\n臺灣中文翻譯：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hackmd.io/@hsiaoa/cybereason-report?fbclid=IwAR0u3u34d9P5Sh2XZGYAG2_BqEF_eFk-OhLOwxPaLzx1cKwEQEbvzNjDxPA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhackmd.io%2F%40hsiaoa%2Fcybereason-report%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0u3u34d9P5Sh2XZGYAG2_BqEF_eFk-OhLOwxPaLzx1cKwEQEbvzNjDxPA&d=Tc8prIKBo9hF1z3tnQ%2BJRtHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=f414245c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hackmd.io/@hsiaoa/cybereason-report?fbclid=IwAR0u3u34d9P5Sh2XZGYAG2_BqEF_eFk-OhLOwxPaLzx1cKwEQEbvzNjDxPA</a><br />\n<br />\nBloomberg 六月廿五號嘅報道：中國「非常可能」已入侵全球十大電信商<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-06-25/global-hack-of-telcos-shows-links-to-china-security-group-says\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2019-06-25%2Fglobal-hack-of-telcos-shows-links-to-china-security-group-says&d=Tc8prIKBo9hF1z3tnQ%2BJRtHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=dfd63f77\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-06-25/global-hack-of-telcos-shows-links-to-china-security-group-says</a>"},{"pid":"d0520ec428be8c36119e6489dd5ab0fe8def4c6d","tid":1294484,"uid":260806,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T19:22:14.000Z","msg":"金融時報報道：China linked to cyber attack on Telegram during Hong Kong protests<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fFes0g1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfFes0g1.png&h=8ff32473&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ft.com/content/57aa24be-8d84-11e9-a24d-b42f641eca37\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F57aa24be-8d84-11e9-a24d-b42f641eca37&d=Tc8prIKBo9hF1z3tnQ%2BJRtHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=8a8b1616\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ft.com/content/57aa24be-8d84-11e9-a24d-b42f641eca37</a>"},{"pid":"d08f2d25e7e2a461001cc5988626eaebf2c23012","tid":1294484,"uid":41344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T19:35:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"601fe6efdc117fcdd7ba5b9f4dfacd445f1cb0fb","tid":1294484,"uid":118805,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T10:44:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets